snippet.title: Apploid Ballfare   Greenlight Trailer
snippet.description:
Apploid: Ballfare is a casual multiplayer sports game that features the combination of rugby and dodgeball elements with grappling hook mechanic.

Music by TeknoAXE : https://youtu.be/URvM6KT5paM
